item.title: [317] Adding Banks [317]
item.dc:creator: @Trxkin Trxkin
item.description:
@Trxkin wrote:

Go to client.java Then press Ctrl > F Then Type in there MakeGlobalObject
After that, Go to http://rspscodes.synthasite.com/object-codes.php And look up the object codes. Once you have found the code, put it in like this. Go on ur client and go to the spot you want that object and type in ::mypos. Once that then type in the X axis and Y axis and 2213 for bank booth.

                                     X        Y    ID     
       makeGlobalObject(2757, 3489, 2213, 0, 10);

I hoped i helped.

Btw 2213 in Bank Booth.

Rep me if i helped.
